---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import GenerativeWaveform from '../components/GenerativeWaveform.tsx';
---

<BaseLayout title="Adam Somers — Creative Technologist">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <GenerativeWaveform client:idle />

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-16">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-8">
        <div class="max-w-2xl flex-1">
          <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4 text-text">
            Hi, it's Adam S.
          </h1>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-text-medium leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Engineering leader in Silicon Valley with a multidisciplinary background in art and technology. Currently senior engineering manager at Apple developing platforms to enable evaluation of AI systems. Musician, tinkerer, dad.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-text-medium leading-relaxed">
            Learn more about my projects and me.
          </p>
        </div>
        <img
          src="/images/coding.PNG"
          alt="Illustration of a person coding with headphones"
          class="w-44 sm:w-56 opacity-70"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Sections -->
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-24 space-y-6">

    <!-- Building -->
    <section class="p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-[10px] border border-border bg-bg" data-animate>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-text">What I'm Building</h2>
        <a href="/building" class="text-sm text-accent hover:underline">Explore &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-text-medium leading-relaxed mb-5">
        My current projects explore the same idea: AI gets dramatically more useful with persistent, structured context. A second mind that knows your ongoing situation, not a chatbot that starts from zero.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <a href="/building/practicepal" class="group block p-4 rounded-[6px] bg-bg-sand hover:bg-bg-deep transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-text group-hover:text-accent transition-colors mb-1">PracticePal</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-medium leading-relaxed">AI music practice companion that remembers your goals, repertoire, and progress across sessions.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/building/fitness-ai" class="group block p-4 rounded-[6px] bg-bg-sand hover:bg-bg-deep transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-text group-hover:text-accent transition-colors mb-1">Fitness AI</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-medium leading-relaxed">Personalized AI trainer that knows your equipment, injuries, and full training history. No more starting from zero.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/building/lead" class="group block p-4 rounded-[6px] bg-bg-sand hover:bg-bg-deep transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-text group-hover:text-accent transition-colors mb-1">Lead Skill for Claude Code</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-medium leading-relaxed">AI-augmented management OS. Persistent file-backed context that makes leadership thinking more durable and grounded.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/building/lead-app" class="group block p-4 rounded-[6px] bg-bg-sand hover:bg-bg-deep transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-text group-hover:text-accent transition-colors mb-1">Lead App <span class="text-xs font-normal text-text-muted">(idea)</span></h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-medium leading-relaxed">Standalone web app version of Lead Skill. Bringing AI-augmented management to a broader audience beyond Claude Code.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Journey -->
    <section class="p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-[10px] border border-border bg-bg" data-animate>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-text">Journey</h2>
        <a href="/journey" class="text-sm text-accent hover:underline">Full timeline &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-text-medium leading-relaxed mb-5">
        Careers that zig and zag are exciting. Mine went from a music technology BFA to senior engineering management at Apple. Audio plugins, a startup, VR pioneering, and big tech. Every pivot built on what came before.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">CalArts BFA</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">&rarr;</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">Audio DSP</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">&rarr;</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">Stanford CCRMA</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">&rarr;</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">Universal Audio</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">&rarr;</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">Startup Founder</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">&rarr;</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">Jaunt VR</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">&rarr;</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">Meta</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-sand text-text-medium">&rarr;</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-[3px] bg-bg-deep text-text font-medium">Apple</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Thinking + Human side by side -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Thinking -->
      <section class="p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-[10px] border border-border bg-bg" data-animate>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-text">Thinking</h2>
          <a href="/thinking" class="text-sm text-accent hover:underline">Read more &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-text-medium leading-relaxed">
          <li><strong class="text-text">AI as a second mind.</strong> Persistent context turns AI from ask-a-question into a system that compounds your thinking over time.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">Creative people make great leaders.</strong> Empathy, vision, taste, comfort with ambiguity. The arts background isn't a detour.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">Growth by stretching.</strong> Assign people into unexpected areas. The only way to grow is beyond where you're comfortable.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Human -->
      <section class="p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-[10px] border border-border bg-bg" data-animate>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-text">Human</h2>
          <a href="/human" class="text-sm text-accent hover:underline">More &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-text-medium leading-relaxed">
          <li><strong class="text-text">Music.</strong> I produce electronic music in experimental, ambient, and psychedelic styles. I also create software tools for music creation and performance.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">Trail running.</strong> I train for ultra marathons on Bay Area trails.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">Tinkering.</strong> Stanford CCRMA portfolio of instruments, plugins, and audio tools. Still building with my hands.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">Family.</strong> I live in the San Francisco Bay Area with my family.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
